República is a Mexican restaurant in Portland, Oregon with a menu based on seasonality - dishes that appear one week might soon be gone as the components change. Spend a day behind the scenes with founder and co-owner Angel Medina and see how he and the staff work to be the best "storytellers" of Mexican food they can be, innovating with modern ideas while ensuring the continuity of tradition.&#13;
